reviews.text:
Been here on 2 occasions where I ordered the Mince pork rice dish and BOTH TIMES I found hair in my food.
First time I found it after eating half of it, they gave me another plate of food when really all I wanted was a refund. Around 6 months later I returned only because I had a work lunch there and ordered the same thing, found hair in it again that definitely looks like a pube. NEVER AGAIN!  !
Liked it the first time but second time was disappointing.  However really liked by other people.
Good Thai food 😍 its our favorite place 😍
Noodles OK but not the chicken rice
Rice not good, pork ok

reviews.text:
湯好淡，面好淋，問佢拎辣椒魚露，居然冇，好似係特登唔比，隔離枱要醋又係冇，咩都冇，重敢自居泰式料理，叫左3寶麵，啲丸係街市果隻丸的水準，70蚊，凍飲加3蚊，又係淡到暈的凍檸茶，
感覺唔好囉😡，邊會冇辣椒，咁大個廚房
醋同魚露都唔會冇囉，最多唔似正常泰國菜咁係一樽樽自家製配好味的，因為依間野都唔係正宗，
比少少廚房用的辣椒黎都好
